{
  "texts": [
    "Effect of Sub-Document-Level Token ReducerIn this section, we investigate the effect of sub-document-level token reducer.",
    "We first conduct an ablation study on it.The results are illustrated in Figure 12.",
    "From this figure, we can see that our proposed token reducer can significantly reduce the input tokens while not decreasing the answering accuracy.",
    "Specifically, compared with the original input tokens, our method can reduce 49% of input tokens on the TriviaQA dataset, 37% on the NQ dataset and 49% on the PopQA dataset.",
    "The results demonstrate the effectiveness of our proposed token reducer.Next, we investigate the impact of the number of documents that are inputted to the token reducer."
  ]
}